{"word":"G3623 - οἰκονόμος - oikonómos - oy-kon-om'-os - Chamberlain","slug":"G3623","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">οἰκονόμος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>oikonómos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>oy-kon-om'-os"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Chamberlain"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BF;&#x03B9;&#x0313;&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x03BD;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03BC;&#x03BF;&#x03C2; - oikonomos</b> - <i>oy-kon-om'-os</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G3624\">G3624</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G3551\">G3551</a>; a <i>house distributor</i> (that is, <i>manager</i>), or <i>overseer</i>, that is, an employee in that capacity; by extension a fiscal <i>agent</i> (<i>treasurer</i>); figuratively a <i>preacher</i> (of the Gospel): - chamberlain, governor, steward."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2026\">G2026</a>, <a href=\"#/G2731\">G2731</a>, <a href=\"#/G2732\">G2732</a>, <a href=\"#/G2733\">G2733</a>, <a href=\"#/G3609\">G3609</a>, <a href=\"#/G3611\">G3611</a>, <a href=\"#/G3613\">G3613</a>, <a href=\"#/G3614\">G3614</a>, <a href=\"#/G3615\">G3615</a>, <a href=\"#/G3616\">G3616</a>, <a href=\"#/G3617\">G3617</a>, <a href=\"#/G3618\">G3618</a>, <a href=\"#/G3619\">G3619</a>, <a href=\"#/G3620\">G3620</a>, <a href=\"#/G3621\">G3621</a>, <a href=\"#/G3622\">G3622</a>, <a href=\"#/G3624\">G3624</a>, <a href=\"#/G4925\">G4925</a>"}]}